int genevalmag::Maglib::gen_evaluator ( const string  path_input_file,
const string  path_folder_output,
const string  name_library,
const vector< string > &  headers,
const string  path 
) const

Generates the static evaluator's files for the Attribute grammar specificated in the input_path_file passed as parameter. All outputs of the library be saved in the path_folder_output. The evaluator classname is defined by name_library. The user could include somes headers for uses externs functions to evaluator.
